description: Coast 2 Coast Deli is two young, eager dudes who grew up on the East Coast, determined to showcase their love and passion for deli style sandwiches!! Coast 2 Coast (“C2C”) is a trendy, urban “city-esque” foodtruck. It’s all about an edgy thinking outside-the-box modern twist on deli sandwiches. C2C is founded on East Coast tradition and being presented in the greater Las Vegas region with a splash of the West. We offer the best of both worlds, meshing the two styles, capturing the best of America’s down home tradition. We created sandwiches that are indigenous to East and West Coast cities allowing the multicultural demographic to feel right at home.
name: Coast 2 Coast Deli
